button.description:
## Description

Bouton d'action du Design System décliné en 4 variantes (`primary`, `secondary`, `ghost`, `danger`) et 3 tailles (`sm`, `md`, `lg`), construit sur un élément `<button>` natif avec layout flex horizontal, icônes optionnelles gauche/droite, et états interactifs complets.

## Spec

- **Géométrie Figma** : rayon `8px` (`--button-radius`), padding horizontal `16px` (sm/md) ou `24px` (lg), padding vertical `4px` (sm) ou `8px` (md/lg), gap `4px` (sm) ou `8px` (md/lg)
- **Typographie Figma** : Inter, `font-weight: 600`, tailles `14px` (sm), `16px` (md), `18px` (lg) — ⚠️ la taille `18px` (lg) n'est pas couverte par `--button-size-lg-font-size` (résolu `16px` dans les tokens) ; la valeur Figma `18px` est conservée via fallback
- **Hauteurs Figma** : `25px` (sm), `35px` (md), `38px` (lg) — différentes des `min-height` token (`32px`, `40px`, `48px`) ; les dimensions Figma priment
- **Icônes** : slot `icon` positionnable à gauche ou à droite, taille `12px` (Figma), entouré d'un wrapper `1px` de padding, visible uniquement si fourni
- **États** : `default`, `:hover`, `:active`, `:disabled` avec `cursor: not-allowed` et `pointer-events: none` via l'attribut natif `disabled`
- **Focus visible** : `outline` `2px` solid `--button-focus-ring-color`, offset `2px`, uniquement sur `:focus-visible`
- **Variante `danger`** : non présente dans `figma.designSpec` (48 enfants couvrent uniquement `primary` et `secondary`) — les tokens `danger` sont présents dans `allowedCssVars` et appliqués conformément aux tokens sémantiques
- **Transition** : `--button-transition` (`all 150ms ease-in-out`) sur tous les états

## Do & Don't

✅ **Do**
- Utiliser `variant="primary"` pour l'action dominante d'une zone, une seule par contexte
- Toujours spécifier `type="button"`, `type="submit"` ou `type="reset"` explicitement
- Passer l'attribut natif `disabled` pour désactiver — pas une prop CSS seule
- Utiliser le slot `icon` uniquement pour les icônes fonctionnelles justifiées

❌ **Don't**
- Ne pas utiliser `<Button>` pour la navigation — utiliser un `<a>` ou un composant `Link`
- Ne pas inventer de variante hors `primary`, `secondary`, `ghost`, `danger`
- Ne pas surcharger le `border-radius` ou les couleurs en dehors des tokens `allowedCssVars`
- Ne pas omettre le `type` sur un bouton dans un formulaire

## Code interactif (Live Editor)

```jsx
const sizeTokens = {
  sm: {
    paddingX: "var(--button-size-sm-padding-x, 16px)",
    paddingY: "var(--button-size-sm-padding-y, 4px)",
    fontSize: "var(--button-size-sm-font-size, 14px)",
    lineHeight: "var(--button-size-sm-line-height, 17px)",
    gap: "var(--button-size-sm-gap, 4px)",
    height: "25px",
    iconSize: "12px",
  },
  md: {
    paddingX: "var(--button-size-md-padding-x, 16px)",
    paddingY: "var(--button-size-md-padding-y, 8px)",
    fontSize: "var(--button-size-md-font-size, 16px)",
    lineHeight: "var(--button-size-md-line-height, 19px)",
    gap: "var(--button-size-md-gap, 8px)",
    height: "35px",
    iconSize: "12px",
  },
  lg: {
    paddingX: "var(--button-size-lg-padding-x, 24px)",
    paddingY: "var(--button-size-lg-padding-y, 8px)",
    fontSize: "var(--button-size-lg-font-size, 18px)",
    lineHeight: "var(--button-size-lg-line-height, 22px)",
    gap: "var(--button-size-lg-gap, 8px)",
    height: "38px",
    iconSize: "12px",
  },
};

const variantTokens = {
  primary: {
    bg: "var(--color-action-primary-bg-default, #d07506)",
    bgHover: "var(--color-action-primary-bg-hover, #1D4ED8)",
    bgActive: "var(--color-action-primary-bg-active, #1E40AF)",
    bgDisabled: "var(--color-action-primary-bg-disabled, #F3F4F6)",
    color: "var(--color-action-primary-text-default, #FFFFFF)",
    colorDisabled: "var(--color-action-primary-text-disabled, #D1D5DB)",
    border: "var(--color-action-primary-border-default, #d07506)",
    borderHover: "var(--color-action-primary-border-hover, #1D4ED8)",
    borderDisabled: "var(--color-action-primary-border-disabled, #F3F4F6)",
  },
  secondary: {
    bg: "var(--color-action-secondary-bg-default, #FFFFFF)",
    bgHover: "var(--color-action-secondary-bg-hover, #F9FAFB)",
    bgActive: "var(--color-action-secondary-bg-active, #F3F4F6)",
    bgDisabled: "var(--color-action-secondary-bg-disabled, #F9FAFB)",
    color: "var(--color-action-secondary-text-default, #374151)",
    colorDisabled: "var(--color-action-secondary-text-disabled, #D1D5DB)",
    border: "var(--color-action-secondary-border-default, #D1D5DB)",
    borderHover: "var(--color-action-secondary-border-hover, #9CA3AF)",
    borderDisabled: "var(--color-action-secondary-border-disabled, #E5E7EB)",
  },
  ghost: {
    bg: "var(--color-action-ghost-bg-default, transparent)",
    bgHover: "var(--color-action-ghost-bg-hover, #F3F4F6)",
    bgActive: "var(--color-action-ghost-bg-active, #E5E7EB)",
    bgDisabled: "var(--color-action-ghost-bg-disabled, transparent)",
    color: "var(--color-action-ghost-text-default, #374151)",
    colorDisabled: "var(--color-action-ghost-text-disabled, #D1D5DB)",
    border: "var(--color-action-ghost-border-default, transparent)",
    borderHover: "var(--color-action-ghost-border-hover, transparent)",
    borderDisabled: "var(--color-action-ghost-border-disabled, transparent)",
  },
  danger: {
    bg: "var(--color-action-danger-bg-default, #DC2626)",
    bgHover: "var(--color-action-danger-bg-hover, #B91C1C)",
    bgActive: "var(--color-action-danger-bg-active, #991B1B)",
    bgDisabled: "var(--color-action-danger-bg-disabled, #F3F4F6)",
    color: "var(--color-action-danger-text-default, #FFFFFF)",
    colorDisabled: "var(--color-action-danger-text-disabled, #D1D5DB)",
    border: "var(--color-action-danger-border-default, #DC2626)",
    borderHover: "var(--color-action-danger-border-hover, #B91C1C)",
    borderDisabled: "var(--color-action-danger-border-disabled, #F3F4F6)",
  },
};

// Minimal SVG icon placeholder (12×12, matches Figma vector stroke)
const IconPlaceholder = ({ color = "currentColor" }) => (
  <svg
    width="12"
    height="12"
    viewBox="0 0 12 12"
    fill="none"
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    aria-hidden="true"
    style={{ display: "block", flexShrink: 0 }}
  >
    <path
      d="M2.5 6h7M6 2.5l3.5 3.5L6 9.5"
      stroke={color}
      strokeWidth="1.2"
      strokeLinecap="round"
      strokeLinejoin="round"
    />
  </svg>
);

const Button = ({
  children,
  variant = "primary",
  size = "md",
  disabled = false,
  icon = null,
  iconPosition = "left",
  type = "button",
  onClick,
}) => {
  const [hovered, setHovered] = React.useState(false);
  const [pressed, setPressed] = React.useState(false);

  const sz = sizeTokens[size];
  const vt = variantTokens[variant];

  const resolvedBg = disabled
    ? vt.bgDisabled
    : pressed
    ? vt.bgActive
    : hovered
    ? vt.bgHover
    : vt.bg;

  const resolvedBorder = disabled
    ? vt.borderDisabled
    : hovered && !pressed
    ? vt.borderHover
    : vt.border;

  const resolvedColor = disabled ? vt.colorDisabled : vt.color;

  const baseStyle = {
    display: "inline-flex",
    flexDirection: "row",
    alignItems: "center",
    justifyContent: "center",
    gap: sz.gap,
    paddingTop: sz.paddingY,
    paddingBottom: sz.paddingY,
    paddingLeft: sz.paddingX,
    paddingRight: sz.paddingX,
    height: sz.height,
    borderRadius: "var(--button-radius, 8px)",
    border: `var(--button-border-width, 1px) solid ${resolvedBorder}`,
    background: resolvedBg,
    color: resolvedColor,
    fontFamily: "var(--button-font-family, Inter, sans-serif)",
    fontSize: sz.fontSize,
    fontWeight: "var(--button-font-weight, 600)",
    lineHeight: sz.lineHeight,
    letterSpacing: "0px",
    cursor: disabled ? "not-allowed" : "pointer",
    transition: "var(--button-transition, all 150ms ease-in-out)",
    outline: "none",
    boxSizing: "border-box",
    userSelect: "none",
    whiteSpace: "nowrap",
  };

  const focusStyle = {
    outline: `var(--button-focus-ring-width, 2px) solid var(--button-focus-ring-color, #3B82F6)`,
    outlineOffset: "var(--button-focus-ring-offset, 2px)",
  };

  const [focused, setFocused] = React.useState(false);
  const mergedStyle = focused ? { ...baseStyle, ...focusStyle } : baseStyle;

  const iconEl = icon ? (
    <span
      style={{
        display: "inline-flex",
        alignItems: "center",
        justifyContent: "center",
        padding: "1px",
        width: sz.iconSize,
        height: sz.iconSize,
        flexShrink: 0,
      }}
    >
      <IconPlaceholder color={resolvedColor} />
    </span>
  ) : null;

  return (
    <button
      type={type}
      disabled={disabled}
      style={mergedStyle}
      onMouseEnter={() => !disabled && setHovered(true)}
      onMouseLeave={() => { setHovered(false); setPressed(false); }}
      onMouseDown={() => !disabled && setPressed(true)}
      onMouseUp={() => setPressed(false)}
      onFocus={() => setFocused(true)}
      onBlur={() => setFocused(false)}
      onClick={!disabled ? onClick : undefined}
    >
      {iconEl && iconPosition === "left" && iconEl}
      <span style={{ display: "inline-block" }}>{children}</span>
      {iconEl && iconPosition === "right" && iconEl}
    </button>
  );
};

// ── Preview Matrix ──────────────────────────────────────────
// Axes: variant × size × disabled
const VARIANTS = ["primary", "secondary", "ghost", "danger"];
const SIZES = ["sm", "md", "lg"];

const sectionLabelStyle = {
  fontFamily: "Inter, sans-serif",
  fontSize: "11px",
  fontWeight: 600,
  color: "#6B7280",
  textTransform: "uppercase",
  letterSpacing: "0.06em",
  marginBottom: "8px",
};

const rowLabelStyle = {
  fontFamily: "Inter, sans-serif",
  fontSize: "11px",
  color: "#9CA3AF",
  width: "72px",
  flexShrink: 0,
  paddingTop: "2px",
};

render(
  <div style={{ padding: "32px", background: "#F9FAFB", fontFamily: "Inter, sans-serif" }}>
    {/* Matrix: variant rows × size columns */}
    <div style={{ marginBottom: "40px" }}>
      <div style={sectionLabelStyle}>Matrice variant × taille (état default)</div>
      {/* Header sizes */}
      <div style={{ display: "flex", alignItems: "center", marginBottom: "12px" }}>
        <div style={{ width: "72px" }} />
        {SIZES.map((s) => (
          <div
            key={s}
            style={{
              width: "120px",
              fontFamily: "Inter, sans-serif",
              fontSize: "11px",
              color: "#6B7280",
              fontWeight: 600,
              textAlign: "center",
            }}
          >
            {s}
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
      {VARIANTS.map((v) => (
        <div key={v} style={{ display: "flex", alignItems: "center", marginBottom: "16px" }}>
